| [`e2e/guests.spec.ts`](file:///c:/Users/olana/OneDrive/Documents/crenelle/e2e/guests.spec.ts) | Guest list, add guest dialog, bulk import |

**To activate E2E tests**, add these to `.env.local`:
```
E2E_TEST_EMAIL=...
E2E_TEST_PASSWORD=...
E2E_TEST_EVENT_SLUG=...   # for registration tests
E2E_TEST_EVENT_ID=...     # for guest tests
```

Then run:
```bash
npx playwright install  # first time only
npm run test:e2e
```

