**To activate Sentry**, add to `.env.local`:
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=https://xxx@oxx.ingest.sentry.io/xxx
SENTRY_DSN=https://xxx@oxx.ingest.sentry.io/xxx
SENTRY_ORG=your-org-slug
SENTRY_PROJECT=crenelle
SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=sntrys_...  # only needed for production builds with source maps
```

Create a new Sentry project at [sentry.io](https://sentry.io) → New Project → Next.js.

See [`.env.sentry-and-tests.example`](file:///c:/Users/olana/OneDrive/Documents/crenelle/.env.sentry-and-tests.example) for all variable descriptions.

